commentary: Groenewald to Aaron Jones, OUT Groenwal is ecstatic! final nail in the coffin for USA as Jones makes his way back to the pavilion. Could not connect the sweep well and hauls out at long leg!

commentary: Groenewald to Jasdeep Singh, OUT Groenewald gets a fifer! darts this one in, possibily getting some drift in towards the batsman and the ball thuds onto the offstump. Jessy stays there bamboozled as he had no answer!This is an emphatic victoy for Namibia!
